<br>
&quot; died.&quot;<br>
<br>
An iksar buddy of mine and I found one of these corpses (by one of the bandit camps) in West Karana. We almost left for splitpaw immediately instead of going to the ogre camp as we intended, interpreting this disturbing discovery to be a bad omen.<br>
<br>
Needless to say, it was.<br>
<br>
Not only did the ogres play soccer with our skulls, but a friendly wandering necromancer showed up to boil my blood during the corpse run. After all this, the enchantress at the gypsy camp in east karana, who conned dubious to my Ikky friend and indifferent to me, enchanted my friend and attempted (unsuccessfully) to kill me. The odd bit being that we had bought and sold at the camp earlier in the day.<br>
<br>
